{"tid":960654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東倒斃家中　終年63歲","createTime":"2018-12-29T14:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T15:10:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddade8801590c23e2884883cc6ce5b477d3e935e","tid":960654,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181229/s00001/c6e420f4ecccc630fffc2a5caac889ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2Fc6e420f4ecccc630fffc2a5caac889ba.jpg&h=d0bc04ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今午4時27分，警方接獲一名女子報案，指其63歲姓林丈夫倒卧寓所牀上。救護接報到場，證實林當場死亡，死因有待驗屍後確定，事件無可疑，案件列作「發現屍體」處理。據了解，死者為著名導演林嶺東。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，1955年出生的林嶺東，先是考入無綫電視藝訓班，未幾轉向幕後發展和一度移民外流，1982年回港拍攝首部電影、譚詠麟主演的《陰陽錯》。到1987、88年，林以《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》和《學校風雲》三部曲成為大紅導演，並憑周潤發主演的《龍虎風雲》，拿下第7屆香港電影金像獎最佳導演。<br />\n<br />\n林嶺東其後亦曾拍攝過《高度戒備》等大片，本世紀初曾嘗試到荷里活發展，回流後近作是2007年跟另外兩名著名導演徐克和杜琪峯合作的《鐵三角》、2015年的《迷城》，和2016年的《沖天火》等。"},{"pid":"23b96f82eaa5aa79dd4f934d8111cb6ed58abafc","tid":960654,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181229/s00001/1546092427610/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2F1546092427610%2F&d=Uy2xpkpjBMQV3%2BMr4GcBXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e29c6132\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2F1546092427610%2F&h=124eccba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181229/s00001/1546092427610/</a>"},{"pid":"3479d2f1cb65805d4a1c829eb8761aa53f2f9f1f","tid":960654,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef464065fa02d197297d812e4f254b84aaa9482b","tid":960654,"uid":48334,"like":0